  "prompt": "Which is the best laptop for around 40k?",
  "response": "As of the latest information available, here are some of the best laptops you can consider for around INR 40,000:\n\n1. **Acer Aspire 3**:\n   - Processor: AMD Ryzen 3 3200U\n   - RAM: 4GB/8GB (expandable)\n   - Storage: 1TB HDD/256GB SSD\n   - Display: 15.6-inch Full HD\n   - OS: Windows 10 Home\n\n2. **HP 15s**:\n   - Processor: Intel Core i3 10th gen or AMD Ryzen 3\n   - RAM: 4GB/8GB (expandable)\n   - Storage: 1TB HDD/256GB SSD\n   - Display: 15.6-inch Full HD\n   - OS: Windows 10 Home\n\n3. **Lenovo Ideapad S145**:\n   - Processor: AMD Ryzen 3 3200U\n   - RAM: 4GB/8GB (expandable)\n   - Storage: 1TB HDD/256GB SSD\n   - Display: 15.6-inch Full HD\n   - OS: Windows 10 Home\n\n4. **ASUS VivoBook 15**:\n   - Processor: Intel Core i3 10th Gen or AMD Ryzen 3\n   - RAM: 4GB/8GB (expandable)\n   - Storage: 1TB HDD/256GB SSD\n   - Display: 15.6-inch Full HD\n   - OS: Windows 10 Home\n\n5. **Dell Inspiron 14 3000**:\n   - Processor: Intel Core i3 10th Gen\n   - RAM: 4GB/8GB (expandable)\n   - Storage: 256GB SSD\n   - Display: 14-inch Full HD\n   - OS: Windows 10 Home\n\nThese laptops provide a good balance of performance and price for everyday tasks such as web browsing, office work, and media consumption. However, prices and availability may vary, so it's advisable to check the latest models, deals, and customer reviews to make an informed decision.",
